WEBVTT

1
01:27:52.450 --> 01:27:54.750 
- 我怎么样决定?  - 我不知道
- How do I decide?  - I don't know.

2
01:27:54.820 --> 01:27:55.710 
我问问题
I ask questions.

3
01:27:55.710 --> 01:27:57.320 
如果回答很有道理
If I get sensible answers,

4
01:27:57.320 --> 01:27:58.750 
他们就能去美国了
then they get to go to America.

5
01:27:58.820 --> 01:28:00.190 
如果没道理 他们就去不了
If I don't, they don't.

6
01:28:00.260 --> 01:28:02.320 
- 有什么不明白的吗?  - 没有
- Anything you don't understand?  - No.

7
01:28:02.390 --> 01:28:03.230 
我再问一次
I ask again,

8
01:28:03.230 --> 01:28:05.050 
你怎么会不穿衣服到这里来?
how you come  to be here with no clothes?

9
01:28:06.460 --> 01:28:08.020 
我穿了件外套
Well, I got an overcoat on.

10
01:28:09.300 --> 01:28:11.230 
- 你是在和我抬杠吗?  - 没有 长官
- Are you jacking with me?  - No, sir.

11
01:28:11.300 --> 01:28:13.360 
- 别和我抬杠  - 是 长官
- Don't jack with me.  - Yes, sir.

12
01:28:13.970 --> 01:28:16.170 
- 你是现役军人吗?  - 不 我是老兵
- You in the service?  - No, I'm a veteran.

13
01:28:16.240 --> 01:28:18.710 
- 越南?  - 是的 长官 去了两次
- 'Nam?  - Yes, sir, two tours.

14
01:28:18.780 --> 01:28:21.370 
- 什么部队?  - 12步兵营
- What outfit?  - Twelfth Infantry Battalion,

15
01:28:21.440 --> 01:28:25.040 
1966年8月7日 1968年7月2日
August 7th, 1966, July 2nd, 1968.

